smul_apply:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr →+ » -/
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr • » -/
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr • » -/
theorem smul_apply (r : R) (f : «expr →+ » A B) (x : A) : («expr • » r f) x = «expr • » r (f x) :=
  rfl
#align smul_apply smul_apply
